luminary, star, personage, distinguished man"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a mountain","examples":[{"text":"أَشْهَرُ مِنْ نَارٍ عَلَى عَلَم","english":"very famous"},{"text":"وَمِنْ آيَاتِهِ ٱلْجَوَارِ فِي ٱلْبَحْرِ كَٱلْأَعْلَامِ"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"proper noun"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"Classical Arabic form of عَالَم (ʕālam)","tags":["Arabic","Classical","alt-of"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ʕa.li.ma/","/ʕal.la.ma/","/ʕilm/","/ʕa.lam/","/ʕaː.lam/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n30346","headword_ar":"عَلْمٌ","root":"Elm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maEolamN","text_ar":"مَعْلَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n30347","headword_ar":"عِلْمٌ","root":"Elm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"is an inf. n., (S, K, &c.,) and [as such] has no pl. [in the classical language]. (Sb, TA voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fikorN","text_ar":"فِكْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".) [As a post-classical term, used as a simple subst., its pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuluwmN","text_ar":"عُلُومٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", signifying The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sciences,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"several species of knowledge."},{"kind":"text","text":"] ―         -b2-  Sometimes it is applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Predominant opinion;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"preponderant belief;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] because it stands in stead of that which is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eilom","text_ar":"عِلْم"},{"kind":"text","text":"properly so termed. (Ham p. 632.) ―         -b3-  And sometimes it is used in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EamalN","text_ar":"عَمَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A doing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.], as mentioned by Az, on the authority of Ibn-'Oyeyneh, agreeably with an explanation of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAlimN","text_ar":"عَالِمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as signifying one “ who does according to his knowledge; ” and it has been expl. as having this meaning in the Kur xii. 68 [where the primary meaning seems to be much more apposite]. (TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laqiytuhu A^adonaY EilomK","text_ar":"لَقِيتُهُ اَدْنَى عِلْمٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I met him the first thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lqyth A^adonaY","text_ar":"لقيته اَدْنَى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dan~iYi","text_ar":"دَنِّىِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adonaY danFA","text_ar":"اَدْنَى دَنًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"; or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"before everything"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"else"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n30348","headword_ar":"عَلَمٌ","root":"Elm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaAmapN","text_ar":"عَلَامَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An impression,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"impress;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a footstep,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"track,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"trace."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  And The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealam","text_ar":"عَلَم"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a garment, or piece of cloth; (S;) [i. e. the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ornamental,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"figured,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"variegated, border"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"borders"},{"kind":"text","text":"thereof;] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"figured,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"variegated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"embroidered, work"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"decoration,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the borders,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,) thereof: (Msb, K, TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEolaAmN","text_ar":"اَعْلَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) ―         -b4-  And ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A way-mark;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing set up,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"erected, in the way,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) or, as in the M,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the deserts,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"waterless deserts,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for guidance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) in the M,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for the guidance of those going astray;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaAmapN","text_ar":"عَلَامَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) the former is also applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a building raised in the beaten track of the road, of such as are places of alighting for travellers, whereby one is guided to the land"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is the object of a journey"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEolaAmN","text_ar":"اَعْلَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalamN","text_ar":"عَلَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manaArap","text_ar":"مَنَارَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. a mistranscription for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manaAr","text_ar":"مَنَار"},{"kind":"text","text":", without"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":": see these two words]. (TA. [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maEolamN","text_ar":"مَعْلَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) [Hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEolaAmu AlkawaAkibi","text_ar":"اَعْلَامُ الكَوَاكِبِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The stars,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"asterisms, that are signs of the way to travellers:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miSobaAHN","text_ar":"مِصْبَاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A separation between two lands;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manaArN","text_ar":"مَنَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":";] as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaAmapN","text_ar":"عَلَامَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEolaAmu AlHarami","text_ar":"اَعْلَامُ الحَرَمِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The limits that are set to the Sacred Territory."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b6-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A mountain;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) as a general term: or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a long mountain:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) [app. as forming a separation: or as being a known sign of the way:] pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEolaAmN","text_ar":"اَعْلَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EilaAmN","text_ar":"عِلَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) the former pl. occurring in the Kur [xlii. 31 and] lv. 24. (TA.) ―         -b7-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A banner,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"standard,"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAyapN","text_ar":"رَايَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to which the soldiers congregate:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and, (K,) some say, (TA,) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flag,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strip of cloth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is tied upon the spear:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) it occurs in a verse of Aboo-Sakhr El-Hudhalee with the second fet-hah lengthened by an alif after it [so that it becomes ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaAm","text_ar":"عَلَام","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (IJ, TA.) ―         -b8-  And (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"chief of a people"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"party:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) from the same word as signifying “ a mountain ” or “ a banner: ” (TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEolaAmN","text_ar":"اَعْلَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b9-  [In grammar, it signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A proper name"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a person or place &c. ―         -b10-  And the pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEolaAmN","text_ar":"اَعْلَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Things pertaining to rites and ceremonies"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the pilgrimage or the like,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as being signs"},{"kind":"text","text":"thereof; such as the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"places where such rites and ceremonies are performed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beasts destined for sacrifice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"various practices performed during the pilgrimage &c.;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maEaAlimu","text_ar":"مَعَالِمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", pl. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maEolamN","text_ar":"مَعْلَمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": the former word is applied to such places in the Ksh and Bd and the Jel in ii. 153; and the latter, in the Ksh and Bd in ii. 194: the former is also applied to the beasts destined for sacrifice in the Ksh and Bd and the Jel in xxii. 37; and the latter, in the Ksh and Bd in xxii. 33: and both are applied to the practices above mentioned, the former in the TA and the latter in the K, in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$Er","text_ar":"شعر"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iEaArN","text_ar":"شِعَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]       -A2-  See also what next follows."}],"source_refs":["Msb","K","TA","S"]}]}}